    <h2>Project Summary: Simple Description</h2>
    <p>
        The **Yireh AI Screenplay Writer** is an innovative, multilingual software designed to help screenwriters, filmmakers, and content creators quickly draft and analyze professional film scripts. It acts as a **smart writing assistant** that enforces strict industry formatting while leveraging the power of free, hosted AI models. Yireh turns a basic story idea (logline) into a professionally formatted, production-ready script segment, complete with essential analysis, all in your language of choice.
    </p>

    <h2>Consolidated Feature List (The Yireh Suite)</h2>
    <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>
            <h3>Phase 1: Core Generation & Formatting</h3>
            Uses hosted free LLMs (e.g., LLaMA 3) with a **Strict Formatting Prompt** to enforce industry-standard structure (Sluglines, Cues, Dialogue, etc.).
            <br>
            **Key Feature:** Multilingual output support (English, Hindi, Tamil, Telugu, Kannada, Malayalam).
        </li>
        <li>
            <h3>Phase 2 & 3: Structural & Production Utility</h3>
            **Beat Sheet Generator:** Maps the script to a standard 15-Beat structure (Plot Points, Midpoint, etc.) for strong narrative foundation.
            <br>
            **Page Breaks:** Automatically enforces page numbering and layout consistency.
        </li>
        <li>
            <h3>Phase 4 & 5: Advanced Analysis & Export</h3>
            **Character Indexing:** Parses the script to generate a **Character Breakdown Report** showing total lines and scene appearances per character (essential for casting/budgeting).
            <br>
            **Basic Budget Estimator:** Scans for high-cost indicators (NIGHT shoots, EXPLOSION, STUNT) and assigns a complexity score for early financial risk assessment.
            <br>
            **HTML Export:** Allows the user to download the generated script and analysis report as a single, shareable, static HTML file.
        </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Yireh Technology Stack (All Free Resources)</h2>
